Annual All Church BBQ at Oaks Park||<h3>Everyone is Invited!</h3>
<h4>August 28, 12:30 - 2:30 PM</h4>
<p>Join us for this awesome annual event at Oaks Park. Right after church, come attend one of the best BBQs around! For those who enjoy amusement rides, you&rsquo;ll be smack dab in the center of all the activities. Free parking and a fun time for all ages makes this one of our favorite events of the year. Make plans to join us!<br /><br /></p>
